+{"id":"frankenpandas-r1k24","title":"fd90.127: MergeExecutionOptions + MergeValidateMode not re-exported from frankenpandas (used in fd90.113 examples)","description":"fd90.74-126 README audit. Merge: Advanced Options examples at README lines 869-897 (fixed in fd90.113) use:
